reviews.text:
I recently ran into an unexpected and serious situation legally, and I knew I had to find a serious attorney to represent me, and I found that with Mr. Daniel Kolacia.
Mr. Kolacia did his absolute best to represent me and my case, kept in good touch, always informing and keeping me in the loop of how my situation was getting handled, he tried any possible way to try to make my case better and getting a chance at a lesser sentence, and I’m very thankful to say that Mr. Kolacia was able to get my felony charge reduced to a misdemeanor, with no time served.(And fortunately my case was a really close call to serious time.) I am so appreciative of the fact that I am able to be home with my family through the holidays, and that’s all thanks to Mr. Daniel Kolacia;
I recommend him to anybody as he is very professional, involved, fair, and overall a great and helpful person. Thank you.
